      "pos": [
        6094,
        6131
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Microsoft.Fabric.Testability.Powershell.dll - the Testability PowerShell module - is installed automatically when you install the Microsoft Service Fabric MSI; and, the module is loaded automatically when you open a PowerShell prompt.",
      "pos": [
        6132,
        6366
      ]
    },
