    {
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>CompleteMode<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> - completion mode specifies that it should not verify whether the restart action actually succeeded; specifying the completion mode as \"Verify\" will cause it to verify whether the restart action actually succeeded.",
      "pos": [
        9389,
